summary: Small simple player home (room) in Riften TG
descriptionHtml:
A player room with all crafting, bed, labeled storage, big aquarium.
Door to it is in the Rat in the Pot, just left of the door to the Cistern.
NOTE! you do need to have access to the Cistern (the secret door has to be open, so do the TG quest for that from Brynjolf).
Or just to view the place if you do not have access yet to the Cistern: use console coc ACtgRetreat

Req: Skyrim + Update
author: Arwen Cire
